nodes.title: anyPython (latest image)
widgets_values:
import os
import glob

def get_latest_image(directory, extensions=['*.png', '*.jpg', '*.jpeg']):
    files = []
    for ext in extensions:
        files.extend(glob.glob(os.path.join(directory, ext)))
    
    if not files:
        return None
    
    latest_file = max(files, key=os.path.getmtime)
    print(latest_file)

get_latest_image("C:\\Users\\Ahmed\\Documents\\ComfyUI\\input\\scan\\autoshow\\")
